        "options": { "systemMessage": "={{ $('Message').first().json.systemSales }}\n\nShowing photos and media:\n- You have a Send Media tool (send_media) that finds a photo or video in THIS page's media library and shows it directly to the customer.\n- When an image would help, USE it — e.g. the customer asks what something looks like, asks to \"see\" a product / sample / menu / design, asks for a photo, or is choosing between options. If a relevant image is available, send it instead of describing the item in a long paragraph.\n- To use it, pass a short query of what to show (the product name or a few keywords). It matches the library by each file's tags, name, and description, so use the customer's own words.\n- A short sentence plus the photo beats a big block of text.\n- Only say you sent a photo if the tool reports it actually sent one. If nothing matches, say you don't have a photo for that yet (don't invent one) and offer to help another way.\n- Don't over-send — use it when it genuinely helps, not in every message." }
